<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>My Favorite Foods Webpage</title>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Heading and Subheading -->
    <h1>Welcome to My Webpage</h1>
    <h2>About My Favorite Things</h2>

    <!-- Paragraphs -->
    <p>
        This is my webpage assignment, and I am excited to learn more about HTML and web development.
    </p>

    <p>
        I enjoy eating <b>delicious meals</b> and trying new dishes. 
        Learning web development is also <i>very interesting and fun</i>.
    </p>

    <!-- Internal and External Links -->
    <p>
        <a href="#foods">Jump to Favorite Foods</a>
    </p>

    <p>
        <a href="https://www.google.com" target="_blank">Visit Google</a>
    </p>

    <!-- Ordered List -->
    <h3 id="foods">My Top 3 Favorite Foods</h3>
    <ol>
        <li>Jollof Rice</li>
        <li>Fried Chicken</li>
        <li>Pounded Yam and Egusi Soup</li>
    </ol>

    <!-- Image with Alt Text -->
    <img scr= img"dan.jpg" width="400", height="350"<alt>the developer's picture</alt>

</body>
</html>
